ieee80211_get_qos_ctl - get pointer to qos control bytes : the frame
The qos ctrl bytes come after the frame_control, duration, seq_num and 3 or 4 addresses of length ETH_ALEN. 3 addr: 2 + 2 + 2 + 3*6 = 24 4 addr: 2 + 2 + 2 + 4*6 = 30
ieee80211_get_SA - get pointer to SA : the frame

Given an 802.11 frame, this function returns the offset to the source address (SA). It does not verify that the header is long enough to contain the address, and the header must be long enough to contain the frame control field.
ieee80211_get_DA - get pointer to DA : the frame

Given an 802.11 frame, this function returns the offset to the destination address (DA). It does not verify that the header is long enough to contain the address, and the header must be long enough to contain the frame control field.
ieee80211_is_robust_mgmt_frame - check if frame is a robust management frame : the frame (buffer must include at least the first octet of payload)
ieee80211_fhss_chan_to_freq - get channel frequency : the FHSS channel
Convert IEEE802.11 FHSS channel to frequency (MHz) Ref IEEE 802.11-2007 section 14.6
ieee80211_freq_to_fhss_chan - get channel : the channels frequency
Convert frequency (MHz) to IEEE802.11 FHSS channel Ref IEEE 802.11-2007 section 14.6
ieee80211_dsss_chan_to_freq - get channel center frequency : the DSSS channel
Convert IEEE802.11 DSSS channel to the center frequency (MHz). Ref IEEE 802.11-2007 section 15.6
ieee80211_freq_to_dsss_chan - get channel : the frequency
Convert frequency (MHz) to IEEE802.11 DSSS channel Ref IEEE 802.11-2007 section 15.6
This routine selects the channel with the closest center frequency.
ieee80211_ofdm_chan_to_freq - get channel center frequency : starting frequency == (dotChannelStartingFactor/2) MHz : the OFDM channel
Convert IEEE802.11 OFDM channel to center frequency (MHz) Ref IEEE 802.11-2007 section 17.3.8.3.2
ieee80211_freq_to_ofdm_channel - get channel : starting frequency == (dotChannelStartingFactor/2) MHz : the frequency
Convert frequency (MHz) to IEEE802.11 OFDM channel Ref IEEE 802.11-2007 section 17.3.8.3.2
This routine selects the channel with the closest center frequency.
ieee80211_tu_to_usec - convert time units (TU) to microseconds : the TUs
